metadata.title: Solution and tools: How much does the evaluation kit cost?

sections.content:
Question:
How much does the evaluation kit cost?
Answer:
The evaluation kit can be provided free of charge for qualified projects. Please contact your Renesas sales representative or our development partner for more information. 
Suitable Products
RISC-V Voice ASSP
